data.description: Welcome to Battery Point, where functionality meets charm. Here, everything you desire is easily accessible, from the array of community amenities to the convenience of nearby shopping. Discover why so many individuals proudly call Battery Point their home.This residence features three bedrooms on the main floor, accompanied by an additional living space, bedroom, and bath on the second floor awaiting your personal touch. While some carpets may require TLC, this allows for your personal preference.With a low-maintenance yard, you'll have more time to relish the community's amenities. Whether it's fishing or boating at the community dock, enjoying a game of tennis, or lounging by the pool, this home and its surroundings offer a multitude of options for leisure and relaxation
